{"html":"<br/>\n<h2>Fact Symbols with Injective Instances</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\">None</p><br/>\n<h2>Multiset Rewriting Rules</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\"><span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> AC) isend:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !KU( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> K( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> AC) irecv:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !KD( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) Register_pk_Bank:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Fr( ~ltkB ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;!Bank_Ltk( $B, ~ltkB ), !Bank_Pk( $B, pk(~ltkB) ), Out( pk(~ltkB) )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) B_1:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( blind(~x, r) ), !Bank_Ltk( $B, ~ltkB ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> Withdraw( ~x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out( sign(blind(~x, r), ~ltkB) ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) S_1:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( &lt;~x, sign(~x, ~ltkB)&gt; ), !Bank_Pk( $B, pk(~ltkB) ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out( &lt;~x, sign(~x, ~ltkB)&gt; ), St_S_1( $B, ~x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) B_2:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( &lt;x, sign(x, ~ltkB)&gt; ), !Bank_Ltk( $B, ~ltkB ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> Deposited( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Private_Ch( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) S_2:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Private_Ch( x ), St_S_1( $B, x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> Spend( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span></p><br/>\n<h2>Restrictions of the Set of Traces</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\"><span class=\"hl_keyword\">restriction</span> BankOnlyAcceptsOnce:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>x #j #k<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Deposited( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">∧</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Deposited( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #k<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>#j <span class=\"hl_operator\">=</span> #k<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">// safety formula</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/*<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;expanded formula:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>x #j #k<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Deposited( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">∧</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Deposited( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #k<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>#j <span class=\"hl_operator\">=</span> #k<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;*/</span></p><br/>\n","title":"Multiset rewriting rules and restrictions"}